data.chText: （文学、艺术、电影或音乐的）体裁，类型
data.enText: a particular type or style of literature, art, film or music that you can recognize because of its special features

means: (文学、艺术、电影或音乐的)类型

tr: a class of art (or artistic endeavor) having a characteristic form or technique
a kind of literary or artistic work
a style of expressing yourself in writing

value.def: A genre is a particular type of literature, painting, music, film, or other art form which people consider as a class because it has special characteristics.

example.ex: ...his love of films and novels in the horror genre.
example.tran: 他对恐怖电影和恐怖小说的热衷

value.tran: （文学、绘画、音乐、电影等艺术作品的）体裁，类型

trans: 风俗画(与17世纪荷兰和佛兰德斯画家有关，取材于日常生活的绘画风格)
